'''''Daar doer in die bosveld''''' (Icyongereza: ''Far Away in Bushveld'' ) niyo film yambere yakozwe [[Afurika y’Epfo|numuyobozi wumunya Afrika yepfo]] Jamie Uys<ref>https://mubi.com/films/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld</ref> . Yasohotse bwa mbere mu 1951. <ref>https://mubi.com/films/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld/cast</ref> Filime iri mu [[Ikinyafurikansi|rurimi rwa Afrikaans]], ururimi rwihariye rwa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>https://muzikum.eu/en/jim-reeves/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld-lyrics</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ni urwenya ku muhinzi ufite isoni witwa Hans Botha usabwa gufata umwarimu ukiri muto witwa Martie du Toit<ref>https://www.fiff.ch/en/daar-doer-die-bosveld</ref>. Hans ageze aho bisi ihagarara gufata Martie arumirwa rwose kubera ubwiza bwe kandi abasha kuvuga gusa interuro<ref>http://www.mimosafilms.co.za/Archive/Film/51/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld</ref>, "It looks like rain.." na It was an accident<ref>https://worldfilmgeek.com/2021/08/12/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld-south-africa-1951/</ref>." Bombi bahura ningorane nyinshi munzira; ahanini bitewe n'imodoka ya kera ya Hans<ref>https://www.songteksten.nl/songteksten/1523431/charles-jacobie/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld.htm</ref>. Igihe bombi bageze aho Martie yerekeza, Martie atose kandi yemeza ko Hans ari igicucu<ref>https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld/HBE,RB9zQmc</ref>. Hans, ariko, akunda byimazeyo Martie<ref>https://mx.napster.com/artist/jim-reeves/album/jim-reeves-country-music-vol-2/track/daar-doer-in-die-bosveld?l=en</ref>. 

